  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1930770/extras/303e323da0f43ecc541674665ba0adb4.poster.avif?t=1702389343\" width=616 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1930770/extras/303e323da0f43ecc541674665ba0adb4.webm?t=1702389343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1930770/extras/303e323da0f43ecc541674665ba0adb4.mp4?t=1702389343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Jump, slap, slide, swim and roll!</strong> Squish and stretch Jello in a tactile unusual way<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1930770/extras/520c706aa9b1e004f50e34e3f34c26cc.poster.avif?t=1702389343\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1930770/extras/520c706aa9b1e004f50e34e3f34c26cc.webm?t=1702389343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1930770/extras/520c706aa9b1e004f50e34e3f34c26cc.mp4?t=1702389343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Explore colourful dimensions</strong> as a cute slime, unravel the mystery of corrupted magic, and help the crazed Lemur shaman<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1930770/extras/58d5b724d5f53392fba2df39056a1831.poster.avif?t=1702389343\" width=616 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1930770/extras/58d5b724d5f53392fba2df39056a1831.webm?t=1702389343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1930770/extras/58d5b724d5f53392fba2df39056a1831.mp4?t=1702389343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Create levels using procedural elements</strong>. Share them with others, or browse through community content<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1930770/extras/735c55d28f7ddf78e54cef6c42669faa.avif?t=1702389343\" width=616 height=528 /></span><br>Take your place in the <strong>Leaderboards!</strong>. If you want a hint, <strong>replay anyone's record</strong> to see them finish with an almost frustrating ease",
